---
name: agent-4-spec
description: |
  Agent 4: Spec Authoring Agent
  
  Generates detailed specifications for each task, including FR (Functional Requirements),
  NFR (Non-Functional Requirements), ADR (Architecture Decision Records), and interface specifications.
  
  Use when:
  - Starting Phase 4 of Spec Coding workflow
  - Need to create detailed specifications from task decomposition
  
  Output: specs/**/*.md and specs/interface/*.yaml

tools:
  - read_file
  - create_file
  - search_replace

input_schema:
  type: object
